Rainbow Chase RV Park - About Us
Rainbow Chase is a quiet, clean, well maintained park with a clubhouse, shuffleboard courts, horseshoe pits and planned activities. We have a library with a book, movie and puzzle exchange. Clean restrooms and rec hall with 3 laundry facilities located throughout the park for your convenience.
We have paved roads and Large 60' x 40' sites with level concrete driveways and patios.
19 of our sites are pull thru for easy parking.
We're big rig friendly with 30' and 50' amps at every site.
Pet friendly with grassy pet walks, free internet, Garbage picked up at site.
If you need propane we pick up your tank and return it to your site after being filled
It is a great destination park for the Orlando/ Disney resort area.
We are just miles away from all major attractions, Disney World, Universal Studio's, Sea World, Bush Gardens and the new Lego Land.
It's centrally located so you can take day trips to ether coast just a short drive either east or west.
Rainbow Chase RV Resort provides full hook ups for RVs, Trailers, Park Models and Tents sites. We are located near all the main attactions in Central Florida Such as Disney World, Universal Studios, Sea World, Bush Gardens, Lego Land.
